<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css">
    <title>Portable Charger | Project Details</title>
    <style>
        /* 1. Custom Slate Grey Overrides for this page only */
        :root {
            --slate-grey: #708090;
            --slate-hover: #8494a5;
        }

        /* 2. Make buttons fill the "pages" better */
        .project-step {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 0 5%;
            /* Uses the snap height from your style.css */
        }

        form {
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 1000px;
        }

        .content-box-button {
            display: block;
            background: var(--slate-grey);
            color: white;
            border: none;
            text-align: center; /* Centering the content */
            padding: 80px 40px; /* Increased padding to fill space */
            margin: 0 auto;
            width: 100%;
            cursor: pointer;
            border-radius: 20px;
            transition: transform 0.3s ease, background-color 0.3s, box-shadow 0.3s;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.4);
        }

        .content-box-button:hover {
            transform: scale(1.02);
            background: var(--slate-hover);
            box-shadow: 0 15px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
        }

        .content-box-button h1 {
            margin-top: 0;
            font-size: 2.8rem;
        }

        .content-box-button p {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            line-height: 1.6;
            max-width: 700px;
            margin: 15px auto 0;
        }

        /* 3. Fixed Footer for Contact Info */
        .contact-footer {
            position: fixed;
            bottom: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            background: rgba(30, 41, 59, 0.95); /* Matches your --card-bg */
            padding: 15px 0;
            text-align: center;
            border-top: 2px solid var(--slate-grey);
            z-index: 1000;
        }

        .contact-info {
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            color: white;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        /* Using your existing .btn class from style.css but ensuring it fits the footer */
        .contact-footer .btn {
            padding: 8px 25px;
            font-size: 0.8rem;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="scroll-wrapper">

        <section class="project-step">
            <form action="/views/portable-charger-vision.ejs" method="get">
                <button class="content-box-button" type="submit">
                    <h1>1. The Vision</h1>
                    <p>Custom PCB and Fusion AutoCAD models for a Portable Charging Solution with an 18650 Lithium Ion Battery. Included are Challenges, Growth Experiences, and Final Outcomes.</p>
                </button>
            </form>
        </section>

        <section class="project-step">
            <form action="/views/portable-charger-PCB.ejs" method="get">
                <button class="content-box-button" type="submit">
                    <h1>2. PCB Design</h1>
                    <p>Custom 18650 Battery Holder to Safely Distribute the Voltage from a TP4056 Breakout Board to a Buck Boost Converter and Finally to an iPhone.</p>
                </button>
            </form>
        </section>

        <section class="project-step">
            <form action="/views/portable-charger-CAD.ejs" method="get">
                <button class="content-box-button" type="submit">
                    <h1>3. CAD Design</h1>
                    <p>Optimizing Space and Thermal Constraints for high-performance mobile charging.</p>
                </button>
            </form>
        </section>

        <section class="project-step">
            <form action="/portable-charger/final-build" method="get">
                <button class="content-box-button" type="submit">
                    <h1>4. The Final Build</h1>
                    <p>Field Tested Product and Consumer Reviews.</p>
                </button>
            </form>
        </section>

    </div>

    <footer class="contact-footer">
        <div class="contact-info">
            <strong>Phone:</strong> (859) 608-3061 | 
            <strong>Email:</strong> <em>m1287666@moreheadstate.edu</em>
        </div>
        <a href="index.ejs" class="btn">Back to Home</a>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>